race.description: Sunshine Coast Shade Sails Mdn Hcp
race.comment: Former Victorian SILK SONIC (5) is unlucky to still be a maiden placing in all three career outings and strikes a very winnable contest here. She's turned in a strong trial since arriving up here in QLD for the Currie barn. Should find this easier than what she faced down south and looks the one they all have to run down. JE REVE (1) is back from a lengthy spell but has tuned up for this with a recent trial placing. The form he showed when last in work was competitive enough for a race like this. QUEEN ARNI (15) has placed two of four over this track and trip and maps well from gate three. In the mix. SHEMAKESMENERVOUS (11) best of the rest while fresh.
